Text: Hi Jeff, Steve Boerner here. I have a very nice GR opportunity to run by you. Free to talk today real quick?
Ok will call you in 2 min

Steve, this week got really busy and we didn’t get more time to talk.  I appreciate the doc you sent and the follow-up you did with several folks.  It’s been a pleasure working with you and I hope your ears were burning on the call time today for the team.  I wish you only the best in your new endeavor and am confident you will be successful.  Please don’t hesitate to reach out in the future and by all means consider me a strong reference for when that time may come.   Best to you and your wife.  

-Jeff
Thank you, Jeff. My family and I really appreciate the warm send off. Lots of kind comments this afternoon coming from the team. Ears were burning yes. Thanks again.
Did you let John G know you were leaving?
Need to reach out to him for something and wanted to level set
Yes we spoke over the phone last week
Great.  Got down selected in Anoka. Demo next week.
Got a second?  I have a question about Westland
Hi Jeff, can talk Monday or Tuesday I’m OOO today and heading out. Happy to talk soon though and help where I can. Can you let me know the question?
